quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  69,38,"Pas nahin, main qasam khata hoon un cheezon ki bhi jo tum dekhte ho"
  69,39,Aur unki bhi jinhein tum nahin dekhte
  69,40,Yeh ek Rasool-e-kareem ka qaul ( speech ) hai
  69,41,"Kisi shayar ka qaul nahin hai, tumlog kam hi iman latey ho"
  69,42,"Aur na yeh kisi kaahin(soothsayer) ka qaul hai , tum log kam hi gaur karte ho"
  69,43,Yeh Rabb-ul alameen ki taraf se nazil huwa hai
  69,44,Aur agar is (Nabi) ne khud ghad kar koi baat hamari taraf mansook ki hoti
  69,45,To hum iska dayan(right) haath padkad letay
  69,46,Aur iski rag-e-gardan (life vein) kaat daalte
  69,47,Phir tum mein se koi (humein)is kaam se rokne wala na hota
  69,48,Dar haqeeqat yeh parheizgar logon ke liye ek naseehat hai
  69,49,Aur hum jante hain ke tum mein se kuch log jhutlane waley hain
  69,50,Aise kafiron ke liye yaqeenan yeh mujeeb-e-hasrat (cause of regret) hai
  69,51,Aur yeh bilkul yaqeeni haqq hai
  69,52,"Pas aey nabi, apne Rubb-e-azeem ke naam ki tasbeeh karo"